Package com.codigofacilito.fastmatrix

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FastMatrixApp
    This is a command-line application for operating with square matrices and vectors quickly.
    FastMatrixApp.JEnvOptions
    Inner class for defining command-line options.
    InverseMatrix
    The InverseMatrix class provides methods to compute the inverse of a matrix.
    MatrixDeterminant
    The MatrixDeterminant class provides methods to compute the determinant of a matrix.
    MatrixOperations
    The MatrixOperations class provides various methods for performing operations on matrices and vectors.
    MatrixSolveSystem
    The MatrixSolveSystem class provides methods to solve a system of linear equations using Gaussian elimination.
    MatrixUtils
    The MatrixUtils class provides a set of utility methods for manipulating matrices and vectors.
    ReadData
    ReadData class provides methods for reading matrices and vectors from the console, converting them to JSON format, and storing them in a JSON file.
